name: Off8Mile-Gao
description:
Trained on the most expressive illustrations of off8mile. I didn't expect the results to be as... visceral as they are, often more exaggerated than even the source material, but the hypernetwork strength acts as a great emotion modulator, whether you're looking for seething hatred, contemptuous disgust, maniacal glee, cataclysmic despair or twisted obsession.

On behalf of the artist of the training images, I should reiterate that this hypernetwork and any images generated with it are strictly for non-commercial purposes only.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description:
Helpful prompts: "crazy eyes, glowing eyes, wide eyed, clenched teeth, disgust, angry, smug grin, yandere trance, despair, scream."

Works best on NAI and art-based models.
